This kernel is the same as the kernel-huge from slackware.
It just have the following additions:
- aufs2 filesystem support : http://aufs.sourceforge.net/ (http://git.c3sl.ufpr.br/gitweb?p=aufs/aufs2-standalone.git;a=snapshot;h=f216afa94d7c8c267ec6b03f5d344f0eebe5c861;sf=tgz)
- xz compression support for squashfs based on the work of Phillip Lougher on the kernel 2.6.38:
  based on the Kongoni patch: http://sourceforge.net/projects/kongoni/files/kongoni/dist/kernel/patch/patch-kongoni-2.6.37.patch.gz/download
